    id: 'prompt-27',
    prompt: 'Contact your campground 48-72 hours before departure to confirm reservation details, check-in procedures, and any last-minute updates or restrictions',
    category: 'action',
    helpText: 'Proactive communication with your campground prevents arrival day surprises and ensures smooth check-in when you\'re tired from travel. Confirm your reservation details, verify check-in times and procedures, ask about any recent changes to facilities or restrictions, and get current weather or road condition updates. This final confirmation step protects your camping plans from unexpected closures or policy changes while demonstrating responsible planning to campground staff.'
  }
];</parameter>
<parameter name="new_string">  {
    id: 'prompt-27',
    prompt: 'Contact your campground 48-72 hours before departure to confirm reservation details, check-in procedures, and any last-minute updates or restrictions',
    category: 'action',
    helpText: 'Proactive communication with your campground prevents arrival day surprises and ensures smooth check-in when you\'re tired from travel. Confirm your reservation details, verify check-in times and procedures, ask about any recent changes to facilities or restrictions, and get current weather or road condition updates. This final confirmation step protects your camping plans from unexpected closures or policy changes while demonstrating responsible planning to campground staff.'
  },
  {
    id: 'prompt-28',
    prompt: 'Research and select appropriate camping clothing layers including base layers, insulation, and rain protection for your expected weather conditions',
    category: 'research',
    helpText: 'Proper clothing planning is essential for comfort and safety since outdoor temperatures can vary dramatically and weather can change quickly. Research the layering system (base layer for moisture management, insulating layer for warmth, shell layer for wind and rain protection) and choose fabrics appropriate for your climate and activity level. This systematic approach to clothing ensures you stay comfortable and dry while avoiding cotton materials that lose insulating properties when wet.'
  }
];</parameter>
